#. Description of the plugin
#: agnosis.php
msgid ""
"Art blooming out of oblivion. Email your art, AI polishes it, the world sees "
"it. A free, federated publishing network for independent artists."
msgstr ""
"Seni bermekaran dari kelupaan. Kirim karya Anda lewat email, AI memolesnya, "
"dunia melihatnya. Jaringan penerbitan federatif gratis untuk seniman "
"independen."

