#: includes/Artist/DepartureNotification.php:68
#, php-format
msgid "Confirm your departure from %s"
msgstr "Konfirmasi kepergian Anda dari %s"

#. translators: 1: artist display name, 2: site name, 3: confirmation URL
#: includes/Artist/DepartureNotification.php:73
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Hi %1$s,\n"
"\n"
"We received a request to remove your account and all your published work "
"from %2$s.\n"
"\n"
"If you made this request, click the link below to confirm. This action is "
"permanent and cannot be undone.\n"
"\n"
"%3$s\n"
"\n"
"If you did not make this request, you can ignore this email — your account "
"remains unchanged.\n"
"\n"
"— %2$s"
msgstr ""
"Hai %1$s,\n"
"\n"
"Kami menerima permintaan untuk menghapus akun Anda dan semua karya yang Anda "
"terbitkan dari %2$s.\n"
"\n"
"Jika Anda yang mengajukan permintaan ini, klik tautan di bawah untuk "
"mengonfirmasi. Tindakan ini bersifat permanen dan tidak dapat dibatalkan.\n"
"\n"
"%3$s\n"
"\n"
"Jika Anda tidak mengajukan permintaan ini, Anda dapat mengabaikan email ini "
"— akun Anda tetap tidak berubah.\n"
"\n"
"— %2$s"

#. translators: %s: site name
#: includes/Artist/DepartureNotification.php:121
#, php-format
msgid "An artist has left %s"
msgstr "Seorang seniman telah meninggalkan %s"

#. translators: 1: artist display name, 2: site name
#: includes/Artist/DepartureNotification.php:126
#, php-format
