msgid ""
"The photo is too bright or washed out. Avoid direct sunlight or flash — "
"diffuse light or shade gives more even tones."
msgstr ""
"Foto terlalu terang atau pudar. Hindari sinar matahari langsung atau flash — "
"cahaya difus atau teduh menghasilkan warna yang lebih merata."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:778
msgid ""
"There is glare or a bright reflection on the artwork. Tilt the canvas "
"slightly or photograph at an angle to eliminate reflections from the surface."
msgstr ""
"Ada silau atau pantulan terang pada karya seni. Miringkan kanvas sedikit "
"atau ambil foto dari sudut untuk menghilangkan pantulan dari permukaan."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:779
msgid ""
"There is a reflection on the artwork surface. Tilt the canvas slightly or "
"change your angle to eliminate it."
msgstr ""
"Ada pantulan pada permukaan karya seni. Miringkan kanvas sedikit atau ubah "
"sudut Anda untuk menghilangkannya."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:781
msgid ""
"The image is blurry. Rest your phone or camera on a stable surface, use the "
"self-timer, and make sure the artwork fills most of the frame so autofocus "
"locks on it."
msgstr ""
"Gambar buram. Letakkan ponsel atau kamera Anda di permukaan yang stabil, "
"gunakan timer otomatis, dan pastikan karya seni memenuhi sebagian besar "
"bingkai agar fokus otomatis menguncinya."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:782
msgid ""
"The image is out of focus. Tap on the artwork on your phone screen before "
"shooting to make sure autofocus locks on it, and hold the camera still."
msgstr ""
"Gambar tidak fokus. Ketuk karya seni di layar ponsel Anda sebelum memotret "
"agar fokus otomatis menguncinya, dan pegang kamera tetap stabil."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:783
msgid ""
"There is motion blur. Hold the camera very still or use a tripod; press the "
"shutter gently or use the self-timer to avoid shake."
msgstr ""
"Ada blur akibat gerakan. Pegang kamera sangat stabil atau gunakan tripod; "
"tekan tombol rana dengan lembut atau gunakan timer otomatis untuk "
"menghindari guncangan."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:784
msgid ""
"Camera shake is visible. Use a tripod or rest the camera on a flat surface "
"and use the self-timer to avoid movement when pressing the shutter."
msgstr ""
"Terlihat getaran kamera. Gunakan tripod atau letakkan kamera di permukaan "
"datar dan gunakan timer otomatis untuk menghindari gerakan saat menekan "
"tombol rana."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:786
msgid ""
"The image resolution is too low. Use your phone's highest quality setting "
"and make sure you're close enough that the artwork fills the frame."
msgstr ""
"Resolusi gambar terlalu rendah. Gunakan pengaturan kualitas tertinggi di "
"ponsel Anda dan pastikan Anda cukup dekat sehingga karya seni memenuhi "
"bingkai."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:787
msgid ""
"The image resolution is too low. Use your phone's highest quality setting "
"and fill the frame with the artwork."
msgstr ""
"Resolusi gambar terlalu rendah. Gunakan pengaturan kualitas tertinggi di "
"ponsel Anda dan penuhi bingkai dengan karya seni."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:788
msgid ""
"The image is pixelated. Shoot from closer or use a higher resolution setting "
"on your camera."
msgstr ""
"Gambar berpiksel. Ambil foto dari jarak lebih dekat atau gunakan pengaturan "
"resolusi yang lebih tinggi pada kamera Anda."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:790
#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:791
msgid ""
"The photo has a strong colour cast. Shoot under neutral daylight or use your "
"phone's Auto White Balance setting for more accurate colours."
msgstr ""
"Foto memiliki dominasi warna yang kuat. Ambil foto di bawah cahaya siang "
"yang netral atau gunakan pengaturan Auto White Balance di ponsel Anda untuk "
"warna yang lebih akurat."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:792
msgid ""
"The photo looks too yellow or warm. Shoot under natural daylight or switch "
"your phone's white balance to Daylight / Cloudy."
msgstr ""
"Foto terlihat terlalu kuning atau hangat. Ambil foto di bawah cahaya siang "
"alami atau ubah white balance ponsel Anda ke Daylight / Cloudy."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:793
msgid ""
"The photo has a cold blue tint. Move the artwork to a warmer, more natural "
"light source or adjust your camera's white balance."
msgstr ""
"Foto memiliki rona biru yang dingin. Pindahkan karya seni ke sumber cahaya "
"yang lebih hangat dan alami atau sesuaikan white balance kamera Anda."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:795
msgid ""
"Part of the artwork appears to be cropped out of the frame. Step back and "
"make sure the entire work is visible before shooting."
msgstr ""
"Sebagian karya seni tampak terpotong dari bingkai. Mundur sedikit dan "
"pastikan seluruh karya terlihat sebelum memotret."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:796
msgid ""
"The artwork is photographed at an angle, causing distortion. Shoot straight "
"on, with the camera parallel to the canvas."
msgstr ""
"Karya seni difoto dari sudut miring, menyebabkan distorsi. Ambil foto dari "
"depan, dengan kamera sejajar dengan kanvas."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:797
msgid ""
"The artwork looks distorted or skewed. Position your camera directly in "
"front of the artwork, parallel to its surface."
msgstr ""
"Karya seni terlihat terdistorsi atau miring. Posisikan kamera Anda tepat di "
"depan karya seni, sejajar dengan permukaannya."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:798
msgid ""
"There is a shadow across part of the artwork. Reposition your light source "
"or move the artwork so no shadows fall on the surface."
msgstr ""
"Ada bayangan melintang pada sebagian karya seni. Posisikan ulang sumber "
"cahaya Anda atau pindahkan karya seni agar tidak ada bayangan jatuh ke "
"permukaan."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:865
msgid ""
"We received your submission, but unfortunately the photo quality is too low "
"for us to show your artwork clearly. We didn't publish it — but please don't "
"be discouraged! A simple retake is usually all it takes."
msgstr ""
"Kami menerima kiriman Anda, tetapi sayangnya kualitas fotonya terlalu rendah "
"untuk menampilkan karya seni Anda dengan jelas. Kami tidak memublikasikannya "
"— tetapi jangan berkecil hati! Mengambil ulang foto biasanya sudah cukup."

#. translators: %d: quality score out of 10
#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:874
#, php-format
msgid "📷 Photo quality score: %d / 10"
msgstr "📷 Skor kualitas foto: %d / 10"

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:880
msgid "Here's what our AI detected and how to fix it:"
msgstr "Berikut yang terdeteksi oleh AI kami dan cara memperbaikinya:"

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:887
msgid ""
"The overall photo quality was too low for our AI to process the artwork "
"clearly."
msgstr ""
"Secara keseluruhan, kualitas foto terlalu rendah untuk diproses AI kami "
"dengan jelas pada karya seni."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:893
msgid "💡 Quick tips for a great artwork photo"
msgstr "💡 Tips cepat untuk foto karya seni yang bagus"

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:895
msgid ""
"Use natural light — position the artwork near a window on a cloudy day for "
"even, soft light."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan cahaya alami — posisikan karya seni dekat jendela pada hari mendung "
"untuk mendapatkan cahaya yang merata dan lembut."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:896
msgid ""
"Shoot straight on — hold your phone parallel to the canvas to avoid "
"perspective distortion."
msgstr ""
"Ambil dari depan — pegang ponsel Anda sejajar dengan kanvas untuk "
"menghindari distorsi perspektif."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:897
msgid ""
"Fill the frame — let the artwork take up most of the shot; crop out "
"distracting backgrounds."
msgstr ""
"Penuhi bingkai — biarkan karya seni mengisi sebagian besar foto; potong "
"latar belakang yang mengganggu."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:898
msgid ""
"Hold still — tap the artwork on your screen to focus, then press the shutter "
"gently or use a self-timer."
msgstr ""
"Tahan tetap — ketuk karya seni di layar Anda untuk fokus, lalu tekan rana "
"dengan lembut atau gunakan timer otomatis."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:903
msgid ""
"Once you have a clearer photo, just email it to the same address as before — "
"we'll pick it up automatically."
msgstr ""
"Setelah Anda memiliki foto yang lebih jelas, cukup kirim email ke alamat "
"yang sama seperti sebelumnya — kami akan mengambilnya secara otomatis."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:908
msgid ""
"Your previous submission is saved in your submissions page in case you want "
"to review what was sent."
msgstr ""
"Pengajuan Anda sebelumnya tersimpan di halaman pengajuan Anda jika Anda "
"ingin meninjau apa yang telah dikirim."

#: includes/Publishing/Notification.php:910
msgid "View submissions →"
msgstr "Lihat pengajuan →"

